Using firefox both for surfing and to develop web apps, i usually have a panorama section with mail and search engines, and another one with developments sites.

The problem comes when i have to reload all the tabs in development section, becose the applications tabs (that are shared between all the panorama sections) get refreshed too.

Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1.Pin few tabs as &quot;application tabs&quot;
2.Open some other &quot;normal&quot; tabs
3.Right-click on a &quot;normal&quot; tab, then click &quot;refresh all tabs&quot;
Actual Results:  
All the tabs get refreshed.

Expected Results:  
Only the normal tabs should get refreshed.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
